de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.winter.datafusion

Class DataFusionStrategy<RecordType extends Matchable & Fusible<SchemaElementType>,SchemaElementType extends Matchable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.winter.datafusion.DataFusionStrategy<RecordType,SchemaElementType>
  • Type Parameters:
    RecordType - the type that represents a record

    public class DataFusionStrategy<RecordType extends Matchable & Fusible<SchemaElementType>,SchemaElementType extends Matchable>
extends Object
    Defines which fuser should be applied and which evaluation rules should be used during data fusion process.
    Author:
    Oliver Lehmberg (oli@dwslab.de)

        fuser - the AttributeFuser that performs the fusion
